    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It's got plenty of life left in it and runs like a dream. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
