    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S features the highly sought-after 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 325 hp with a linear power band that rewards high-rev engagement. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the mechanical connection is unfiltered. The mid-engine architecture provides an exceptional polar moment of inertia, further enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono package for optimized throttle mapping. Maintenance is current, including a recent ignition coil replacement and a brake fluid flush with high-boiling-point fluid. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with road use, the chassis remains stiff, the shift linkage is tight, and the engine exhibits no signs of bore scoring or oil consumption. This is a driver\u2019s specification optimized for mechanical feedback and apex hunting.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
