    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-specific subframe and lightweight aluminum suspension geometry. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through the M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and bottom end. The exterior retains its aerodynamic profile with the factory carbon fiber roof intact, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offers variable damping rates to suit both daily transit and high-lateral-G maneuvers. A true enthusiast-spec example with solid mechanical foundations.",
      "price": 34500.0,
